snippet.title: First Game Boy Game Released In 20 Years | Dimeo's Jukebox | Official Trailer
snippet.description:
Introducing the first Game Boy game released in 20 years! Step into the jukebox with the first ever music album released on Game Boy, along with a challenging adventure/ puzzle game! It's your choice to unlock each song, or just step into the jukebox right away and listen to some chiptune goodness. Pre-order NOW! Ships December 1st 2020. Subscribe and follow for more details and updates.
